org.springframework.vault.support

Class CertificateBundle

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.vault.support.CertificateBundle

  • public class CertificateBundle
extends Object
    Value object representing a certificate bundle consisting of a private key, the certificate and the issuer certificate. Certificate and keys can be either DER or PEM encoded. DER-encoded certificates can be converted to a KeySpec and X509Certificate.
    Author:
    Mark Paluch
    See Also:
    getPrivateKeySpec(), getX509Certificate(), getIssuingCaCertificate()
